comments: This is my favorite. It’s no-frills. There's no carefully constructed soothing music. Just the voice of the guide with clear directions.
One of the best, if not the best, body scan meditation I’ve come across. You guided the attention in a gentle and expert way. Loved every minute of it. Thank you so much!
I've been doing this practice for 7 years. it's the only meditation that I've found really helps me be calm and collected

This let's me get through my day without breaking down or giving up. Thank you.
